的動作。<br />\n<br />\n「啪啪啪!!!!!!!!!!!」<br />\n<br />\n鮑姐見狀大喜，忽然淫蕩地看著棋靈王......<br />\n<br />\n棋靈王一看她便知其意，面有難色地說: 「鮑鮑聽話，等你黎左m先!」<br />\n只見鮑姐一副失望的表現，<br />\n喃喃自語地道 : 「人地想幫你含撚啫...衰人黎嘅&gt;&lt;」<br />\n<br />\n你看著那個士兵與宇宙漿性交，嘴色露出淫蕩的笑容，細聲地說 : 「大力啦...大力d!!!! 屌咁撚細力! 」<br />\n<br />\n你竟毫不發覺，你已經被解放軍重重包圍。<br />\n當你發現的時候，已經太遲...<br />\n<br />\n「把他們拿下! 」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你們被解決軍捉拿，移送到一所監獄...<br />\n<br />\n你被關在一個單人囚房。<br />\n<br />\n忽然，一個熟悉的身影在解放軍的人群中走過...<br />\n<br />\n她是....<br />\n<br />\n(A)司棋姐<br />\n(B)張曦雯"},{"pid":"243db6b083cf4f20c185fe84b191a4b243428cbc","tid":2201614,"uid":139251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48e42976905c27f81b91578d3413d10eaf57f20c","tid":2201614,"uid":97486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"【忍左好耐】【包包】某女歌星和我的一霎光輝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:41:33.000Z","msg":"唔該樓主 我諗得你明俾人撚既感受"},{"pid":"2dcb5a4c08133708ef29ad0d1f056cc583d0c255","tid":2201614,"uid":139251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7496f2ccf8509d0fcb229b6067915dd5ffe80db","tid":2201614,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"374bec39ca0baff75830b73e8dc113d178186acf","tid":2201614,"uid":139251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fec22c03fe89d9db9ce414d8bc8e47b050358a1","tid":2201614,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:18:16.000Z","msg":"有個咩又屌思棋姐又屌gem果個故呀嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"姐係邊個呀巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:30:52.000Z","msg":"【FF丨互動】假如你是林鄭月娥的老公<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/937292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/937292</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T18:41:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"f02333cf3a3eeb570c2996a8ddfc5ea588afc45b","tid":2201614,"uid":139251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a8a9d03de7aebb8f82469d77a23edf7c2baad2d","tid":2201614,"uid":97486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime